snippet.title: KHYAAL RAKHYA KAR - Neha Kakkar ft. RohanPreet Singh | Anshul Garg | Babbu | Rajat Nagpal |
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents KHYAAL RAKHYA KAR by the Queen Neha Kakkar ft. RohanPreet Singh. 

Listen it on - üéµ
iTunes: https://music.apple.com/in/album/khyaal-rakhya-kar-single/1545300108
Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/khyaal-rakhya-kar-1

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/2RKGtM8v2JM72Gyo1wLmgg?si=gZeZ6u96SP2pwUnXNb4E1w
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/in/album/khyaal-rakhya-kar-single/1545300108
Wynk: https://wynk.in/u/1Y0tgtj97

Singer - Neha Kakkar 
Music - Rajat Nagpal 
Lyrics - Babbu
Sarangi Harpinder kang
Recorded by Rahul Sharma @AMV assisted by Samir Dharap

Featuring - Neha Kakkar & Rohanpreet Singh

Producer - Anshul Garg

Directors - Agam Mann & Azeem Mann
Concept & Screenplay : Neha Kakkar 
Video Supervisor - Raghav Sharma
DOP - Shinda Singh
Choreographer - John
Project Manager - Piyush Chandok 
Childhood Neha - Guddu 
Childhood Rohanpreet - Aarush
Production - Rahul
DI - Onkar Singh
Art Director - Blacc
ADs - Jogi, Ashish Uppal, Jass Panesar, Ravi Goyal
Child Artist casting - Elvin Art Academy Rajpura
Children - Ghazal, Rihanna, Kashvi, Saanvi, Eshanya, Kayanna, Nitya, Deepali, Inayat, Vrinda, Komal, Kavya,Vanya, Tanishtha, Drishti, Prince, Samar, Harshit, Himanshu, Viraj, Kairav, Aarav, Morfin, Garv, Gurshan, Namish, Kanishek
College boy - Money Romana
Artwork - Vicky Sandhu Design
Distribution: Believe Digital
Promotions : Underdog Digital

Lyrics :

Tu trump de warga hain
Main obame wargi han
Tenu kyun lagda hai main
Kise drame wargi han
Tu cheez pyari hai ehnu sambhaal rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain tu apna khyaal rakhya kar

Gallan wich laake tu taj mehal vikaa sakdan
Jinna tu jhootha hain politics ch jaa sakdan
Methon na sach chupaaya kar
Jithe jana daske jaya kar
Main fer tenu kuch nai kehndi
Kuch khaan nu laike aaya kar
Te ghanta ghanta waiting wich na call rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain tu apna khyaal rakhya kar

Tu brad pitt vadda na geriyan laaya kar
J kudi naal meeting hai Mainu naal lejaaya kar
Tenu kudiyan nal milaunde ne
Tere dost hi tenu pilaunde ne
Ah kaisa rang karaaya hai
Tenu ki ki oh sikhaunde ne
Chote hi changey lagde chote vaal rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain Tu apna khyaal rakhya kar


#KhyaalRakhyaKar #NehaKakkar #RohanPreet

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

localizations.en.title: Daddy Yankee - CORONA | Freestyle (Official Video)
localizations.en.description:
Daddy Yankee 
CORONA | Freestyle (Official Video)

At the beginning of the pandemic I wrote this song, however at that moment several thoughts stopped me from presenting it to you. First, I did not want them to think that I was taking advantage of such a difficult situation and, likewise, at that time my physical condition was not the best as I had gained almost 50 pounds. Today, several months later, we are still living in the pandemic and, although we would like to think of it that way, nothing has changed.

It was not my best moment nor that of many, so today I present ‚ÄúCORONA‚Äù so that together we can reflect on what really matters: being alive, being healthy and being grateful for what we have. I, I let my physical condition stop me at that moment but with this video I leave that behind and I understood that the change comes when you decide. Enjoy ‚ÄúCORONA‚Äù in the hope that this chapter of our lives will close very soon!

snippet.title: Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE
snippet.description:
Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE , I'm sure a lot of you have been waiting for this...

This video I go over a recent video made by the Speedrun Mod team that claims that the odds that I got a series of drops over the span of a week is 1 in 7.5 trillion, and therefore came to the conclusion that I must have cheated. This video is meant to refute these claims. I encourage everyone to watch until the end, especially if they watched the original video.

In this video we hear from a statistical expert with a PhD that wrote a 19 page analysis on what the mods did wrong. I also disprove some of the claims made in the original video. All relevant information should be viewable below.

Although I would have loved to attempt to refute the math myself, I suck at math and would have looked like a complete idiot. So, that's where an expert comes in.

Expert's Report & Analysis - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yfLURFdDhMfrvI2cFMdYM8f_M_IRoAlM/view?usp=sharing

World File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pfA1HVWkROlFRG4egWh0GYV5SpbJGozR/view?usp=sharing

Tutorial for viewing level.dat, go to https://irath96.github.io/webNBT/ , and upload the "level.dat" file from the folder there. You can see the raw contents on the right, and an easy to use GUI on the left.

Jar File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OEuu6PWAbhYo3BlUT2hL8mM_aiVPa9Yu/view?usp=sharing
This can be decompiled using a "Java Decompiler", but the modified dates can be verified on your computer.

Thank you to Willz for giving a statement in this video.

All revenue made from this video is being donated to the Minecraft Java Edition Speedrun Mod Team in order to fund development of an anti-cheater speedrun client.

Generally, speedrunning is a past time of mine and is a lot of fun. I mostly look forward to the funny moments with my friends, and the challenge that it presents for me.

Music From:
Audioblocks,
Lemmino - Cipher: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0q5PR1xpA0
Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio

snippet.title: Kilauea Eruption Day Four - Rising Lava Lake Update (Dec. 24, 2020)
snippet.description:
As of just after 7 a.m. Thursday morning, the lava lake surface is was 1,483 feet below the crater rim observation site, indicating that the lake is 554 feet deep. Scientists estimate the lake rose 39 feet in just under 24 hours. 

A synthesized voice was utilized in the narration for this story. Video and photos are from the USGS Hawaiian Volcano Observatory.

snippet.title: BUCKS at CELTICS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 23, 2020
snippet.description:
BUCKS at CELTICS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 23, 2020

Jayson Tatum (30 PTS, 7 REB) knocked down a three-pointer with 0.4 seconds in the game to cap off the 122-121 win for the Boston Celtics over the Milwaukee Bucks. Jaylen Brown led the Celtics in scoring with 33 PTS and 5 REB, while Jeff Teague (19 PTS) and Tristan Thompson (12 PTS, 8 REB) provided a spark in their Boston debuts. Reigning #KiaMVP Giannis Antetokounmpo (35 PTS, 13 REB) Khris Middleton (27 PTS, 14 REB, 8 AST) and Jrue Holiday (25 PTS, 6 REB) combined for 87 of Milwaukee‚Äôs points.

snippet.title: What did I make the HACKSMITH for Christmas?  With Estefannie Explains it All!
snippet.description:
It's time for Maker's Secret Santa, and I got randomly selected the Hacksmith. I also received a present from Estefannie Explains it All!  I decided the Hacksmith needed a Superhero Alert System which uses a deep learning model running on an NVIDIA Jetson Nano 2GB to detect 'superheroes'.  Check out the Hackismith's video to see if it works, and check out Estefannie Explains it All to see how she made my robot gift. All channels that took part are:

Playlist of all Makers' gifts: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBsfTOjKcQe-duagTS5o2rx5vzthE5BZt

Hacksmith: https://www.youtube.com/theHacksmith
Estefannie Explains It All: https://www.youtube.com/estefanniegg
Look Mum No Computer: https://www.youtube.com/LOOKMUMNOCOMPUTER/
Kids Invent Stuff: https://www.youtube.com/KidsInventStuff/
Allen Pan: https://www.youtube.com/SufficientlyAdvanced/
Colin Furze: https://www.youtube.com/colinfurze/
This Old Tony: https://www.youtube.com/featony

You can support me on Patreon or buy my Merchandise:
***************************
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/xrobots
Merchandise: https://teespring.com/stores/james-bruton
***************************

Affiliate links - I will get some money of you use them to sign up or buy something:
***************************
Matterhackers 3D printing supplies: http://www.matterhackers.com?aff=7500
Music for your YouTube videos: http://share.epidemicsound.com/xrobots
***************************

Other socials:
***************************
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xrobotsuk
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/xrobotsuk/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/xrobotsuk 
***************************

CAD and Code for my projects: https://github.com/XRobots

Huge thanks to my Patrons, without whom my standard of living would drastically decline. Like, inside out-Farm Foods bag decline. Plus a very special shoutout to Lulzbot, Inc who keep me in LulzBot 3D printers and support me via Patreon.

HARDWARE/SOFTWARE

Below you can also find a lot of the typical tools, equipment and supplies used in my projects:

Filament from: https://www.3dfuel.com/

CNC Router: https://bit.ly/2QdsNjt

Why not join my community, who are mostly made up of actual geniuses. There‚Äôs a Facebook group and everything: https://www.facebook.com/groups/287089964833488/

XROBOTS

Former toy designer, current YouTube maker and general robotics, electrical and mechanical engineer, I‚Äôm a fan of doing it yourself and innovation by trial and error. My channel is where I share some of my useful and not-so-useful inventions, designs and maker advice. Iron Man is my go-to cosplay, and 3D printing can solve most issues - broken bolts, missing parts, world hunger, you name it.

XRobots is the community around my content where you can get in touch, share tips and advice, and more build FAQs, schematics and designs are also available.

snippet.title: Christmas Sugar Cookies - You Suck at Cooking (episode 120)
snippet.description:
Christmas cookies, sugar cookies, and cookies have one thing in common: you can find them all on planet earth, which is the fifth largest planet in our solar system. 

Subscribe:  http://bit.ly/1HuynlY
YSAC Book + Merch: http://yousuckatcooking.com
http://instagram.com/yousuckatcooking
https://twitter.com/yousuckatcookin

¬Ω pound softened butter
1 cup of sugar 
cream them together with your gyrowangucopterlator 

Then add: 
1 jangled egg 
3 tablespoons milk
1 teaspoon of vanilla extract 
then rejangle with your handheld copterwangler 

In another bowl sift together: 
3 cups all purpose flour 
¬æ teaspoon baking powder 
1 teaspoon salt 

then dump the baking snow onto your butter cloud and recopterize with your 
dough typhoon but feel free to fold it together with your spatulator first to avoid a dust storm 

At this point you should have dough but if you doughn't then add another tablespoon of milk until you have dough (and if you have goo try adding some more wheat dust)

lay the dough down to sleep on plastic wrap (one folded sheet) then throw it in the 
temperature reducer for an hour or two 

then remove it from the heat remover and if it's really cold let it warm up a bit, otherwise start 
pressing and rolling it out until it's ¬º inch thick unless your'e not making cookies

then just do your thing, you know, making shapes and whatnot and bake them for 12 minutes on 350 

If you want to make icing take 1 cup of powdered sugar and add a couple teaspoons of corn syrup and a couple teaspoons of water...you can add more corn syrup and less water or just keep adding corn syrup, it's really up to you. I did one where all I added was maple syrup and that was interesting although you can barely taste the maple over the powdered sugar, but what I learned from this is holy cow does corn syrup ever taste good. As an adult I've been in this mentality that corn syrup is the worst and why would you ever eat that and I tasted it for the first time in years and it was like eating caramel for the first time. I think I chugged that stuff when I was a kid and wanted candy because it's liquid candy. Anyway, what I'm saying is I recommend corn syrup. Even though it comes from corn, which is not recommended.
snippet.tags: ['sugar cookies', 'Christmas cookies', 'cookies', 'recipe', 'chef', 'kitchen', 'how to', 'tutorial', 'baking', 'icing', 'frosting', 'you suck at cooking', 'ysac']

snippet.title: Robot Barber V2. Just mess my stuff up.
snippet.description:
The first 1000 people to use this link will get a free trial of Skillshare Premium Membership: https://skl.sh/stuffmadehere12201
Please consider supporting these projects through my patreon: http://patreon.com/stuffmadehere Although very fun, these videos are very time consuming and expensive.
I use a glowforge pro for rapid prototyping and it's great. You can $500 off a Glowforge pro here: http://glowforge.com/stuffmadehere 

-----------

It was time to take another pass on the hair cutting robot. The new robot is bigger, better, way more reliable and travel friendly. I tried to cut MatPats hair (live) then my brothers hair and then my own. For some reason I'm compelled to improve the pattern carving functionality even though I have zero desire to actually use it....

One final thing - if you know of any actual problems that could use a better solution please leave a comment. One of my goals is to make a portion of my projects attempts at solving legitimately useful problems and I would love to have a good list of them. Thanks!

snippet.title: Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE
snippet.description:
Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE , I'm sure a lot of you have been waiting for this...

This video I go over a recent video made by the Speedrun Mod team that claims that the odds that I got a series of drops over the span of a week is 1 in 7.5 trillion, and therefore came to the conclusion that I must have cheated. This video is meant to refute these claims. I encourage everyone to watch until the end, especially if they watched the original video.

In this video we hear from a statistical expert with a PhD that wrote a 19 page analysis on what the mods did wrong. I also disprove some of the claims made in the original video. All relevant information should be viewable below.

Although I would have loved to attempt to refute the math myself, I suck at math and would have looked like a complete idiot. So, that's where an expert comes in.

Expert's Report & Analysis - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yfLURFdDhMfrvI2cFMdYM8f_M_IRoAlM/view?usp=sharing

World File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pfA1HVWkROlFRG4egWh0GYV5SpbJGozR/view?usp=sharing

Tutorial for viewing level.dat, go to https://irath96.github.io/webNBT/ , and upload the "level.dat" file from the folder there. You can see the raw contents on the right, and an easy to use GUI on the left.

Jar File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OEuu6PWAbhYo3BlUT2hL8mM_aiVPa9Yu/view?usp=sharing
This can be decompiled using a "Java Decompiler", but the modified dates can be verified on your computer.

Thank you to Willz for giving a statement in this video.

All revenue made from this video is being donated to the Minecraft Java Edition Speedrun Mod Team in order to fund development of an anti-cheater speedrun client.

Generally, speedrunning is a past time of mine and is a lot of fun. I mostly look forward to the funny moments with my friends, and the challenge that it presents for me.

Music From:
Audioblocks,
Lemmino - Cipher: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0q5PR1xpA0
Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio

snippet.title: I was very angry with Dele Alli | Stoke 1-3 Tottenham | Jose Mourinho press conference
snippet.description:
TIMESTAMPS
0:00 Intro
0:20 Solid performance but for a period it was 1-1 
1:05 We deserved to win and Son scored a goal that should have counted
1:25 were you angry with Dele for losing possesion? Yes, a player in that position has to link and create, and not create problems for his own team. Yes I was upset
2:30 Gareth Bale told me he was injured and could not come out for 2nd half
3:30 To win this trophy we need to win 2 very difficult matches
5:05 Did Winks, Sanchez or Dele, take their chances tonight? Some yes, some no. Most important thing was the team performance not individuals

snippet.title: Inside Binging With Babish‚Äôs New Brooklyn Home & Studio | Open Door | Architectural Digest
snippet.description:
Today Architectural Digest is welcomed by Andrew Rea from Binging With Babish and the Babish Culinary Universe for a tour of his beautiful new house and production studio. After discovering his work on a previous episode of Open Door, Andrew teamed with interior designer Kyle O‚ÄôDonnell of Gramercy Design to plan his own bohemian home - and the results are spectacular. The fully-equipped production studio on the lower levels of the building are a familiar background to viewers but it‚Äôs in the residence above where the design work truly shines. A magnificent kitchen to match his culinary skills, bright sunlit rooms and a backyard to grill and smoke to his heart‚Äôs content all add up to a pad perfectly tailored to Babish. 

Check out Andrew Rea's newly rebranded channel, Babish Culinary Universe here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJHA_jMfCvEnv-3kRjTCQXw.

And his signature product line with Gibson USA will be available Feb 1! Follow his instagram for more: https://www.instagram.com/bingingwithbabish/

snippet.title: What did I make the HACKSMITH for Christmas?  With Estefannie Explains it All!
snippet.description:
It's time for Maker's Secret Santa, and I got randomly selected the Hacksmith. I also received a present from Estefannie Explains it All!  I decided the Hacksmith needed a Superhero Alert System which uses a deep learning model running on an NVIDIA Jetson Nano 2GB to detect 'superheroes'.  Check out the Hackismith's video to see if it works, and check out Estefannie Explains it All to see how she made my robot gift. All channels that took part are:

Playlist of all Makers' gifts: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBsfTOjKcQe-duagTS5o2rx5vzthE5BZt

Hacksmith: https://www.youtube.com/theHacksmith
Estefannie Explains It All: https://www.youtube.com/estefanniegg
Look Mum No Computer: https://www.youtube.com/LOOKMUMNOCOMPUTER/
Kids Invent Stuff: https://www.youtube.com/KidsInventStuff/
Allen Pan: https://www.youtube.com/SufficientlyAdvanced/
Colin Furze: https://www.youtube.com/colinfurze/
This Old Tony: https://www.youtube.com/featony

You can support me on Patreon or buy my Merchandise:
***************************
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/xrobots
Merchandise: https://teespring.com/stores/james-bruton
***************************

Affiliate links - I will get some money of you use them to sign up or buy something:
***************************
Matterhackers 3D printing supplies: http://www.matterhackers.com?aff=7500
Music for your YouTube videos: http://share.epidemicsound.com/xrobots
***************************

Other socials:
***************************
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xrobotsuk
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/xrobotsuk/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/xrobotsuk 
***************************

CAD and Code for my projects: https://github.com/XRobots

Huge thanks to my Patrons, without whom my standard of living would drastically decline. Like, inside out-Farm Foods bag decline. Plus a very special shoutout to Lulzbot, Inc who keep me in LulzBot 3D printers and support me via Patreon.

HARDWARE/SOFTWARE

Below you can also find a lot of the typical tools, equipment and supplies used in my projects:

Filament from: https://www.3dfuel.com/
Lulzbot 3D Printers: http://bit.ly/2Sj6nil
Lincoln Electric Welder: https://bit.ly/2Rqhqos
CNC Router: https://bit.ly/2QdsNjt
Ryobi Tools: http://bit.ly/2RhArcD
Axminster Micro Lathe: http://bit.ly/2Sj6eeN
3D Printer Filament: http://bit.ly/2PdcdUu
Soldering Iron: http://bit.ly/2DrNWDR
Vectric CNC Software: http://bit.ly/2zxpZqv

Why not join my community, who are mostly made up of actual geniuses. There‚Äôs a Facebook group and everything: https://www.facebook.com/groups/287089964833488/

XROBOTS

Former toy designer, current YouTube maker and general robotics, electrical and mechanical engineer, I‚Äôm a fan of doing it yourself and innovation by trial and error. My channel is where I share some of my useful and not-so-useful inventions, designs and maker advice. Iron Man is my go-to cosplay, and 3D printing can solve most issues - broken bolts, missing parts, world hunger, you name it.

XRobots is the community around my content where you can get in touch, share tips and advice, and more build FAQs, schematics and designs are also available.

Below you can also find a lot of the typical tools, equipment and supplies used in my projects:

Filament from: https://www.3dfuel.com/

Why not join my community, who are mostly made up of actual geniuses. There‚Äôs a Facebook group and everything: https://www.facebook.com/groups/287089964833488/

XROBOTS

Former toy designer, current YouTube maker and general robotics, electrical and mechanical engineer, I‚Äôm a fan of doing it yourself and innovation by trial and error. My channel is where I share some of my useful and not-so-useful inventions, designs and maker advice. Iron Man is my go-to cosplay, and 3D printing can solve most issues - broken bolts, missing parts, world hunger, you name it.

XRobots is the community around my content where you can get in touch, share tips and advice, and more build FAQs, schematics and designs are also available.

snippet.title: Official Dick Whittington ‚Äì A Pantomime for 2020 | Free National Theatre Full Performance
snippet.description:
Watch our pantomime Dick Whittington, a hilarious and heartfelt new version of the classic tale that's packed with the cheekiest of jokes, the chattiest of animals, the awesomest of songs and the messiest of silliness. It's been freshly updated by Jude Christian and Cariad Lloyd for 2020.

Join in our Great British Panto Party at home to help us celebrate the joy and laughter that panto brings to thousands of families across the UK every year.

Dick Whittington is streaming for free from 3pm UK time on Wednesday 23 December 2020. It will be available on demand until midnight UK time on Sunday 27 December.  
 
You need to start watching by 9.45pm UK time on Sunday to be able to watch it all. 

Join us from 5pm UK time after the premiere on 23 Dec for a post-show talk with the cast: https://youtu.be/Ew5keyRcYFc
 
Dick Whittington is recommended for ages 6+. Get involved with the fun, with craft activities for the family using our Panto Party Pack: https://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk/sites/default/files/dick-whittington-panto-pack-v2.pdf
 
The running time is 2hrs 5mins with a short interval. It is subtitled. 
 
The full list of cast and creatives for Dick Whittington is available here: https://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk/shows/dick-whittington 
 
Dick Whittington was filmed live on stage at the National Theatre during its fourth preview performance on Tuesday 15 December 2020.  While Government restrictions prevented the final stages of work on the show, we‚Äôre incredibly proud of everyone involved for working so hard to capture the production at such short notice.
 
Dick Whittington will be available to rent, or with a subscription, for six weeks on our new streaming platform, National Theatre at Home from 11 January 2021. Unmissable theatre, any time, anywhere: https://www.ntathome.com 
--  
Pantomime brings joy and laughter to thousands of families across the UK and we are so excited to share ours with you this Christmas.  
 
We're making Dick Whittington available to watch for free in honour of the many venues who, like us, have been forced to cancel their Christmas shows this year.  
 
If you can, please support your local theatre by donating or booking tickets for 2021.  
 
If you‚Äôd like to support us, you can donate here: https://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk or send a text to 70470 PANTO 5 to donate ¬£5, PANTO 10 to donate ¬£10, or PANTO 20 to donate ¬£20.
 
Texts cost your donation amount plus one standard rate message. UK Networks only.  
 
All donations made to the fundraiser will be generously matched by a National Theatre donor. This means your support will have double the impact.  
 
#NationalTheatre #Pantomime #DickWhittington  
--  
 
Subscribe on YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/c/NationalTheatreOnline  
Sign up to our monthly newsletter: https://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk/register/nt-news  
National Theatre TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@nationaltheatre 
National Theatre Twitter: https://twitter.com/NationalTheatre  
National Theatre Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/nationaltheatre  
National Theatre Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nationaltheatre  
National Theatre Live Twitter: https://twitter.com/NTLive  
National Theatre Live Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ntlive/ 
-- 
Thank you to the amazing artists who have allowed us to share Dick Whittington in this way, during this unprecedented time, when so many pantomime fans can't visit their local theatres. 
 
At the National Theatre in London, we make world-class theatre that is entertaining, challenging and inspiring. And we make it for everyone. 
 
National Theatre Live is National Theatre‚Äôs ground-breaking project to broadcast the best of British theatre to cinemas in the UK and internationally. 
 
Originally commissioned by the Lyric Hammersmith Theatre.

snippet.title: PART 2 | ANG KWENTO SA LIKOD NG VIRAL VIDEO NG MAG-INA AT PULIS SA TARLAC.
snippet.description:
Part 1: https://youtu.be/6snHWZrz4LM

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 12M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | ARSENAL 1-4 MAN CITY | CARABAO CUP
snippet.description:
Holders Manchester City produced another Carabao Cup masterclass as we secured a comprehensive last-eight victory over Arsenal in North London to march into the semi-finals.

Second-half strikes from Riyad Mahrez, Phil Foden and Aymeric Laporte made it a night to remember after Gabriel Jesus‚Äôs third-minute opener had been cancelled out before the break.

The victory further extended manager Pep Guardiola‚Äôs incredible record in the League Cup and was no less than we deserved after what was another impressive all-round display.

snippet.title: PART 1 | VIRAL VIDEO NG SINAPIT NG MAG-INA SA KAMAY NG ISANG PULIS, INAKSYUNAN!
snippet.description:
Part 2: https://youtu.be/Xvs007vv8YY

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 12M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: EVERTON 2-1 ARSENAL | PREMIER LEAGUE HIGHLIGHTS
snippet.description:
Everton made it three wins in a row to move up to second in the Premier League table, beating Arsenal 2-1 at Goodison Park. Dominic Calvert-Lewin thought he'd scored the opener - later credited as an own goal - before Yerry Mina struck just before the break after Nicholas Pepe had levelled from the penalty spot.

snippet.title: Glitterbomb 3.0 vs. Porch Pirates
snippet.description:
Merry Christmas ya filthy animals.  If you want to learn the design fundamentals it takes to make something like the Glitter Bomb, enroll in my NEW Creative Engineering course at https://Monthly.com/MarkRober and I'll see you in class!

MY NEW MERCH!!!  https://markrober.store/

Thanks to SimpliSafe for providing the cameras.  Check out their biggest sale of the year by visiting http://simplisafe.com/markrober

Subscribe to Jim's channel here- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBNG0osIBAprVcZZ3ic84vw

Biodegradable glitter courtesy of  https://www.altnaturals.com/pages/glitter

So stoked to finally announce my creative engineering class has just launched today! Enrollment is now open until Dec 27 at Monthly.com/MarkRober (link also in bio).

This class is a hands-on, 30-day learning experience that will teach you how to use engineering and science to bring your creative ideas to life.

During this class, I'm going to share with you my entire creative engineering process from start to finish. You're going to follow along with me as I fully design and engineer 3 brand new builds from scratch... from how I come up the idea, all the way through bringing the final builds to life.

The best part is, over the month, you'll follow along with me and my process, side by side, and you will leave the class with 3 original, creative builds of your own.

This is the class I wish I had when I was starting out. It's designed to take your skills to make cool stuff to the next level, whether you're a beginner or a more experienced maker/engineer.

The class officially starts on January 4, 2021, and it will only run a few times per year, so claim your spot if you're interested!

See you in class!

-Mark

snippet.title: PART 3 | NAIWANG PAMILYA NG MAG-INA SA TARLAC, BIBIGYAN NG TULONG NI IDOL RAFFY!
snippet.description:
Part 1 link: https://youtu.be/6snHWZrz4LM

Part 2 link: https://youtu.be/Xvs007vv8YY

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 12M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: Mental Health, Suicidal Thoughts and Being A Content Creator ft. Wengie | Find A Way #WithMe
snippet.description:
Joined by one of our favourite YouTubers (and personal friend) Wengie, we dive deep into mental health in the world of content creation. In a time when everyone is facing demons of their own, it's more important than ever to understand how and what we're feeling and to seek the support we need. 

This video does not, and is not intended to contain medical advice in any form. If you are looking for support or help, please approach a licensed medical health professional.

For more resources around mental health in Singapore please see the links below:
Visit https://mindline.sg for mental wellness resources, tips and self-help tools
Have a CHAT (https://www.chat.mentalhealth.sg/) with someone if you need help
Hear from experts at Calm Collective‚Äôs (https://www.calmcollective.asia/) virtual talks and connect with all things youthful on Youthopia (https://youthopia.sg/)

This video was created in collaboration with YouTube. For more mental health and wellbeing tips, please see this playlist: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn0rQERHHwFbl4kprGeo9aCub3Ta_lumi

00:00 - Introduction
00:40 - Tell me about the first time you realised how mentally damaging your work could be for you.
03:00 - What was your most destructive way of coping with stress?
04:30 - What was your darkest moment ever while working in the industry?
08:06 - Tell me the most difficult pill to swallow about coping with your mental health.
09:37 - What was the most helpful thing someone told you when you were struggling?
12:08 - What is the healthiest way you've learnt to cope with stress from work?
13:47 - Give us one tip for how we can cope with heavy mental stress.
15:17 - What is one thing that reminds you why you stay in this industry?
18:50 - Closing

snippet.title: Staying Silent For 22 Years | Find A Way #WithMe
snippet.description:
All of us have secrets but for some of us, our secrets are darker. This episode of Heart On My Sleeve, Liz bravely comes forward to share her past and dark secret. Her mental health was affected and it eventually drove her suicidal. Watch the video to know how she managed to get herself out of this pit-hole. 

*WARNING*
This video may contain disturbing topics and may not be suitable for younger audiences. Viewer discretion is advised. 

This video does not, and is not intended to contain medical advice in any form. If you are looking for support or help, please approach a licensed medical health professional. For more resources around mental health in Singapore, please see the links below:

Visit mindline.sg for mental, wellness resources, tips & self-help tools.
Have a CHAT (https://www.chat.mentalhealth.sg/) with someone if you need help 
Hear from experts from at Calm Collective's (https://www.calmcollective.asia/) virtual talks and connect with all things youthful on Youthopia (https://youthopia.sg/)

snippet.title: EXTENDED CARABAO CUP HIGHLIGHTS: EVERTON 0-2 MAN UNITED
snippet.description:
Everton suffered late, late heartbreak in the Carabao Cup quarter-final as Manchester United struck twice in the closing moments to knock the Blues out. Gylfi Sigurdsson had the best chances for Carlo Ancelotti's side, but Edinson Cavani and Anthony Martial had the final say as the clock ticked down.

snippet.title: Glitterbomb 3.0 vs. Porch Pirates
snippet.description:
Merry Christmas ya filthy animals.  If you want to learn the design fundamentals it takes to make something like the Glitter Bomb, enroll in my NEW Creative Engineering course at https://Monthly.com/MarkRober and I'll see you in class!

MY NEW MERCH!!!  https://markrober.store/

Thanks to SimpliSafe for providing the cameras.  Check out their biggest sale of the year by visiting http://simplisafe.com/markrober

Subscribe to Jim's channel here- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBNG0osIBAprVcZZ3ic84vw

Biodegradable glitter courtesy of  https://www.altnaturals.com/pages/glitter

So stoked to finally announce my creative engineering class has just launched today! Enrollment is now open until Dec 27 at Monthly.com/MarkRober (link also in bio).

This class is a hands-on, 30-day learning experience that will teach you how to use engineering and science to bring your creative ideas to life.

During this class, I'm going to share with you my entire creative engineering process from start to finish. You're going to follow along with me as I fully design and engineer 3 brand new builds from scratch... from how I come up the idea, all the way through bringing the final builds to life.

The best part is, over the month, you'll follow along with me and my process, side by side, and you will leave the class with 3 original, creative builds of your own.

This is the class I wish I had when I was starting out. It's designed to take your skills to make cool stuff to the next level, whether you're a beginner or a more experienced maker/engineer.

The class officially starts on January 4, 2021, and it will only run a few times per year, so claim your spot if you're interested!

See you in class!

-Mark

This class is a hands-on, 30-day learning experience that will teach you how to use engineering and science to bring your creative ideas to life.

During this class, I'm going to share with you my entire creative engineering process from start to finish. You're going to follow along with me as I fully design and engineer 3 brand new builds from scratch... from how I come up the idea, all the way through bringing the final builds to life.

The best part is, over the month, you'll follow along with me and my process, side by side, and you will leave the class with 3 original, creative builds of your own.

This is the class I wish I had when I was starting out. It's designed to take your skills to make cool stuff to the next level, whether you're a beginner or a more experienced maker/engineer.

The class officially starts on January 4, 2021, and it will only run a few times per year, so claim your spot if you're interested!

See you in class!

-Mark

snippet.title: PART 2 | ANG KWENTO SA LIKOD NG VIRAL VIDEO NG MAG-INA AT PULIS SA TARLAC.
snippet.description:
Part 1: https://youtu.be/6snHWZrz4LM

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 12M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: The Beatles:  Get Back - A Sneak Peek from Peter Jackson
snippet.description:
PETER JACKSON REVEALS SNEAK PEEK OF HIS UPCOMING MUSIC DOCUMENTARY
‚ÄúTHE BEATLES: GET BACK‚Äù ONLINE AND STREAMING ON DISNEY+ 

Feature-Length Film Opens in Theatres August 27, 2021

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson has released an exclusive sneak peek of his upcoming documentary ‚ÄúThe Beatles: Get Back‚Äù for fans everywhere to enjoy. The 5-minute special look is available to fans worldwide on TheBeatles.com and streaming on Disney+.
 
Jackson said, ‚ÄúWe wanted to give the fans of The Beatles all over the world a holiday treat, so we put together this five-minute sneak peek at our upcoming theatrical film ‚ÄòThe Beatles: Get Back.‚Äô We hope it will bring a smile to everyone‚Äôs faces and some much-needed joy at this difficult time.‚Äù

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Beatles: Get Back‚Äù is a unique cinematic experience that takes audiences back in time to The Beatles‚Äô intimate recording sessions during a pivotal moment in music history... 

Read more at https://www.thebeatles.com/news/beatles-get-back-sneak-peek-peter-jackson

#TheBeatlesGetBack

Photo by Linda McCartney / ¬© Paul McCartney

snippet.title: Ken Block Vs Rob Dahm!? 1,240hp 4 Rotor AWD RX-7 is our Wildest Battle Yet // Hoonicorn Vs the World
snippet.description:
A race 6 years in the making! When Rob Dahm first saw the Hoonicorn launched in 2014, he knew one thing for sure: he needed that same kind of insane project in his life. Measuring pixel by Instagram pixel, and a few phone calls posing as a Hoonigan employee (thanks, Rob), he went down a path of no return to build the wildest FD RX-7 ever. Four rotors, AWD, a giant turbo, sequential transmission, and a whole lot of learning leads up to this very race: up against the car that inspired him to begin with.

snippet.description:
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a good person B) 
Roomie ‚û§ https://www.youtube.com/user/RoomieOfficial
Behind the scene video ‚û§  https://youtu.be/6H9IrDn5jGE
Animation breakdown ‚û§ https://youtu.be/2tCnN1d4Lj8
SPOTIFY: https://open.spotify.com/album/0nIO2BsGVth75m8XMJBcRG

Music production by BAASIK
Vocal production by ILLBERG
Mixed by BAASIK
Mastered by Bj√∂rn Engelmann

GetMadz ‚û§ https://www.youtube.com/user/TheMadz2012 
Rushlight Invader ‚û§ https://www.youtube.com/user/RushLightInvader 
Annie Loomis ‚û§ https://twitter.com/annieloomisart 
Hexrin ‚û§ https://twitter.com/hexriin 
Funymony ‚û§ https://www.youtube.com/user/funymony 
Nine Doodles ‚û§ https://twitter.com/NineDoodles 
Lollergator ‚û§ https://twitter.com/lollergator 
Julia Klimas ‚û§ https://twitter.com/Julobster 
Vintagecoyote ‚û§ https://twitter.com/vintagecoyote 
Jessica McGinnis ‚û§ https://twitter.com/jaykittens 
Galloame ‚û§ https://www.instagram.com/p/B6mvXBKjR1o/
ServalSketch ‚û§ https://twitter.com/ServalSketch

Lyrics
I‚Äôm at the supermarket
Gon cop some rhubarb
I reach into my pocket
It‚Äôs time to get charged
I pay in cash, and I know what happens next is strange
I flash a stunning smile and say:
‚ÄúYou can keep the change‚Äù
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
You can have that money (It‚Äôs yours!)
And also coins are uncomfortable in my pockets, uh

Sitting by my computer
Mom comes inside the lair
‚ÄúIt‚Äôs smelling like a sewer
You should go and get some air‚Äù
I‚Äôm gettin up, and stretch, I‚Äôm filling up with pride
I open up the door and put a single foot outside
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I leave my house (So healthy!)
I‚Äôm gonna put my foot back inside of my house now, uh

My lifestyle‚Äôs quite unhealthy
I snacked recording this
Got an expanding belly
Can‚Äôt find a shirt that fits
Roll my chair to the kitchen, fill my snack bowl to the brim
Yeah I know that might look bad, but then I sign up for a gym
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I‚Äôm a gym member (gon get ripped)
And I will go there sometime, I just haven‚Äôt decided on a date yet, uh

I‚Äôm chilling out in class
My teacher‚Äôs such a jerk
And suddenly he asks
‚ÄúWhere is your homework‚Äù
All my friends in panic, ‚Äúno was that today??‚Äù
I slap mine on the desk and say ‚ÄúI‚Äôm gonna get an A. Plus.‚Äù
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I do my homework (model student!)
Turns out I plagiarized and now I‚Äôm in detention, uh (sad, whiny uh)

My mom is back again
‚ÄúCan you take out the trash?‚Äù
Her mind was blown right then
‚ÄúI did it before you asked‚Äù
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I do my chores (For mommy!)
Couldn‚Äôt find a trashcan so I dumped it in the ocean, uh

It‚Äôs just a regular day
OR IS IT, grandma?
No, someone‚Äôs changin age and
it isn‚Äôt grandpa
Other grandsons may just write on facebook walls
But I am grandmas special boy, so I am gonna call
OH, what, oh yeah I‚Äôm a good person
I remember birthdays (for example February 7th!)
You better think of me when you‚Äôre drafting up your will

I‚Äôm hanging out with Quinston
He is the coolest guy
Got 30k on insta
Always wears suit and tie
I tell him ‚Äòbout how good I am, but he says ‚Äúbro, 
The people who are really good don‚Äôt brag about it though‚Äù
what? You‚Äôre saying bragging about the nice things you‚Äôve done misses the whole point of doing nice things in the first place?
Oh! What? Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a good person?
I don‚Äôt brag ever (never did!)
Now please excuse me while I go delete my twitter, uh
(Oh, and I gotta delete this song. What, it‚Äôs already on YouTube and Spotify? Well hopefully no one will listen to it.)

Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
You can have that money (It‚Äôs yours!)
And also coins are uncomfortable in my pockets, uh

Sitting by my computer
Mom comes inside the lair
‚ÄúIt‚Äôs smelling like a sewer
You should go and get some air‚Äù
I‚Äôm gettin up, and stretch, I‚Äôm filling up with pride
I open up the door and put a single foot outside
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I leave my house (So healthy!)
I‚Äôm gonna put my foot back inside of my house now, uh

My lifestyle‚Äôs quite unhealthy
I snacked recording this
Got an expanding belly
Can‚Äôt find a shirt that fits
Roll my chair to the kitchen, fill my snack bowl to the brim
Yeah I know that might look bad, but then I sign up for a gym
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I‚Äôm a gym member (gon get ripped)
And I will go there sometime, I just haven‚Äôt decided on a date yet, uh

I‚Äôm chilling out in class
My teacher‚Äôs such a jerk
And suddenly he asks
‚ÄúWhere is your homework‚Äù
All my friends in panic, ‚Äúno was that today??‚Äù
I slap mine on the desk and say ‚ÄúI‚Äôm gonna get an A. Plus.‚Äù
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I do my homework (model student!)
Turns out I plagiarized and now I‚Äôm in detention, uh (sad, whiny uh)

My mom is back again
‚ÄúCan you take out the trash?‚Äù
Her mind was blown right then
‚ÄúI did it before you asked‚Äù
OH!! WHAT
Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a GOOD PERSON
I do my chores (For mommy!)
Couldn‚Äôt find a trashcan so I dumped it in the ocean, uh

It‚Äôs just a regular day
OR IS IT, grandma?
No, someone‚Äôs changin age and
it isn‚Äôt grandpa
Other grandsons may just write on facebook walls
But I am grandmas special boy, so I am gonna call
OH, what, oh yeah I‚Äôm a good person
I remember birthdays (for example February 7th!)
You better think of me when you‚Äôre drafting up your will

I‚Äôm hanging out with Quinston
He is the coolest guy
Got 30k on insta
Always wears suit and tie
I tell him ‚Äòbout how good I am, but he says ‚Äúbro, 
The people who are really good don‚Äôt brag about it though‚Äù
what? You‚Äôre saying bragging about the nice things you‚Äôve done misses the whole point of doing nice things in the first place?
Oh! What? Oh yeah, I‚Äôm a good person?
I don‚Äôt brag ever (never did!)
Now please excuse me while I go delete my twitter, uh
(Oh, and I gotta delete this song. What, it‚Äôs already on YouTube and Spotify? Well hopefully no one will listen to it.)

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 8 Breakdown THANK YOU LUCASFILM
snippet.description:
This was a gift for the soul.

I'll post the write up starting from the big scene

spoilers

Well, it‚Äôs not jus an x-wing. It‚Äôs Luke skywalker. This meant the world to me. Over 35 thousand of you attended the watch party last night and we all shared a moment together as Star Wars fans that I‚Äôll never forget. Luke Skywalker arrives and makes the dark troopers look like absolutely nothing. He wasn‚Äôt even moving fast, it was easy work for a jedi knight like him. Or at this point, a Jedi Master ready to build his roster of students. 

We see a cloaked figure walk through the halls, his movements and lightsaber form very much like Luke Skywalker. Luke used a variation of different lightsaber forms. Mainly form iv Ataru which he learned from master Yoda. However when he used his emotions to fight his father on the second Death Star in return of the jedi, he was using more form v, which was Anakin‚Äôs lightsaber form. He also learned a bit of form 3, soresu from obi-wan in episode 4. This helps with blocking blaster bolts. There‚Äôs a scene here where Luke uses the same move as Anakin against the b-1 battle droid on Mustafar, with the blaster bolt behind the back. Luke comes to the hallway which was a lot like his father against the rebels in rogue one. Grogu just watches the screen amused. Luke dances with his blade, blocking bolts and slicing through the troopers. He uses force pull, force push, and force freeze topped off with force crush. Now this is huge, because force crush was a force power that was a big no no for jedi, however, there was a grey area when using it on droids, or any non living being. Windu and Anakin both used this in the original 2D clone wars back in 2003. Mace uses it on Grievous, which is why he always coughs. And Anakin uses it on Nelvaan against the scientist techno union guy.

The droids and danger has been eliminated by Luke Skywalker. I can‚Äôt believe I‚Äôm saying that. I won‚Äôt get tired of it. Din opens the door and Luke Skywalker steps through the green lit fog by his lightsaber. 
Are you a Jedi.
Yes, he says.

As a de aged mark Hamill, just like I wished would happen, stands there, removing his hood.

He reaches out to grogu, and summons the child. Grogu asks permission from Din, and we get a beautiful poetic scene of Din holding the kid and removing his helmet. This echoes Vader removing his helmet to see his son, Luke. As Din stares at the closest thing to a son he has, and tells Grogu to go, and not be afraid. 

Grogu is placed on the floor as he finally waddles over to R2-D2, who shakes with excitement, recognizing Grogu from Yoda‚Äôs species, but also, a theory that he knows Grogu from the Jedi Temple during the prequels, as we know Grogu was trained as a Jedi at the temple for many years by many masters. He must have known Anakin, or of him at least, as they are the same age. 

Luke Grabs Grogu, takes a good look at him, and bids his farewell to everyone. May the force be with you, as Din cries watching them leave. The doors close from afar as R2 stands next to Luke Skywalker holding Grogu. End of season

Until, the end credits scene!

Tatooine. Jabba‚Äôs palace. Fennec shand kills gammorean guards as she comes down the steps with Boba to follow a few steps behind. Bib Fortuna sits atop Jabba‚Äôs throne. Telling Boba how he had heard rumours of his return. Boba kills him. Big Fortuna was Jabba‚Äôs top secretary and right hand man. We see him in return of the Jedi, and I thought he died, but I guess Boba isn‚Äôt the only one to return from the dead. 
He‚Äôs played here by Matthew Wood, who voices General Grievous in the clone wars. Boba walks up, throws his dead corpse off, and takes his rightful place on the throne of the underworld king. Jabba was the law of the underworld. If scum and villainy. Boba now takes that mantle. He and Fennec will now control the galaxy‚Äôs underworld at their fingertips. The Book of boba, coming December 2021. This is the big question. Will this be a new show all on it‚Äôs own. Having chapters for episodes like the mandalorian. Or will this be what the new mandalorian will be about. Now it‚Äôs about the book of Boba. The first two seasons were about Din and the child, and now it‚Äôs about Boba for a season or two. I‚Äôm inclined to believe it‚Äôs two separate shows that we‚Äôll get at the same time. As the mandalorian season 3 comes end of December 2021 as well. 

Well, and with that. Star Wars has never been more alive. This episode meant so much to me, seeing Luke return the way he did. I can only imagine where it‚Äôll lead us. I think we‚Äôll see Grogu train with Luke, and become a powerful Jedi, and he‚Äôll eventually reunite Grogu with his species, well before Kylo destroys Luke‚Äôs temple. I know a lot of people were asking if Kylo kills Grogu, and I Just can‚Äôt see that happening.


Become a Patron to support future content - https://www.patreon.com/StarWarsTheory

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8CbFnDTYkiVweaz8y9wd_Q/join

He also learned a bit of form 3, soresu from obi-wan in episode 4. This helps with blocking blaster bolts. There‚Äôs a scene here where Luke uses the same move as Anakin against the b-1 battle droid on Mustafar, with the blaster bolt behind the back. Luke comes to the hallway which was a lot like his father against the rebels in rogue one. Grogu just watches the screen amused. Luke dances with his blade, blocking bolts and slicing through the troopers. He uses force pull, force push, and force freeze topped off with force crush. Now this is huge, because force crush was a force power that was a big no no for jedi, however, there was a grey area when using it on droids, or any non living being. Windu and Anakin both used this in the original 2D clone wars back in 2003. Mace uses it on Grievous, which is why he always coughs. And Anakin uses it on Nelvaan against the scientist techno union guy.

The droids and danger has been eliminated by Luke Skywalker. I can‚Äôt believe I‚Äôm saying that. I won‚Äôt get tired of it. Din opens the door and Luke Skywalker steps through the green lit fog by his lightsaber. 
Are you a Jedi.
Yes, he says.

As a de aged mark Hamill, just like I wished would happen, stands there, removing his hood.

He reaches out to grogu, and summons the child. Grogu asks permission from Din, and we get a beautiful poetic scene of Din holding the kid and removing his helmet. This echoes Vader removing his helmet to see his son, Luke. As Din stares at the closest thing to a son he has, and tells Grogu to go, and not be afraid. 

Grogu is placed on the floor as he finally waddles over to R2-D2, who shakes with excitement, recognizing Grogu from Yoda‚Äôs species, but also, a theory that he knows Grogu from the Jedi Temple during the prequels, as we know Grogu was trained as a Jedi at the temple for many years by many masters. He must have known Anakin, or of him at least, as they are the same age. 

Luke Grabs Grogu, takes a good look at him, and bids his farewell to everyone. May the force be with you, as Din cries watching them leave. The doors close from afar as R2 stands next to Luke Skywalker holding Grogu. End of season

Until, the end credits scene!

Tatooine. Jabba‚Äôs palace. Fennec shand kills gammorean guards as she comes down the steps with Boba to follow a few steps behind. Bib Fortuna sits atop Jabba‚Äôs throne. Telling Boba how he had heard rumours of his return. Boba kills him. Big Fortuna was Jabba‚Äôs top secretary and right hand man. We see him in return of the Jedi, and I thought he died, but I guess Boba isn‚Äôt the only one to return from the dead. 
He‚Äôs played here by Matthew Wood, who voices General Grievous in the clone wars. Boba walks up, throws his dead corpse off, and takes his rightful place on the throne of the underworld king. Jabba was the law of the underworld. If scum and villainy. Boba now takes that mantle. He and Fennec will now control the galaxy‚Äôs underworld at their fingertips. The Book of boba, coming December 2021. This is the big question. Will this be a new show all on it‚Äôs own. Having chapters for episodes like the mandalorian. Or will this be what the new mandalorian will be about. Now it‚Äôs about the book of Boba. The first two seasons were about Din and the child, and now it‚Äôs about Boba for a season or two. I‚Äôm inclined to believe it‚Äôs two separate shows that we‚Äôll get at the same time. As the mandalorian season 3 comes end of December 2021 as well. 

Well, and with that. Star Wars has never been more alive. This episode meant so much to me, seeing Luke return the way he did. I can only imagine where it‚Äôll lead us. I think we‚Äôll see Grogu train with Luke, and become a powerful Jedi, and he‚Äôll eventually reunite Grogu with his species, well before Kylo destroys Luke‚Äôs temple. I know a lot of people were asking if Kylo kills Grogu, and I Just can‚Äôt see that happening.

snippet.title: Squishy Makeovers: Spin The Wheel | Fixing Your Squishies #25
snippet.description:
Welcome to another episode of squishy makeovers, where I transform ugly, used, old, dirty, cheap or unwanted squishies (donated by my subscribers) into my own creations. I repair, paint and cut away for hours on end to complete these. Fixing and giving makeovers to squishies is such a fun painting project, and a great creative art activity. It's been keeping me busy for years üòÇ Hopefully you like my creations this episode. Get used to lots of rainbow and sprinkles, because I am addicted to both!


_________FAQs__________

1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?
So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.

2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?
No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they were damaged, and no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. It would be waaay too complicated/expensive and massively time consuming to keep track of everyone and return each squishy. I'm just one person! 

3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?
I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.

5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?
The matte fabric paint is more likely to crack after lots of squishing. Slick fabric paints never crack. But there are benefits to both. I usually mix the two paints together to get the best of both worlds.

6. CAN I USE ACRYLIC PAINT ON SQUISHIES?
I would not recommend that. Acrylic paint will either make the squishy hard, or it will crack and flake off very easily. 


___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh üòÇ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.



___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Every Friday at 4:00pm ET: Alternating Squishy Makeovers, Thrift Makeovers, Craft Kit Reviews, Create This Book, Mail Openings and Miscellaneous crafts and DIYs

snippet.title: Truck Driver Who Hit Cyclists Says He Fell Asleep at the Wheel
snippet.description: New bodycam footage has been released in the fatal truck crash that killed five cyclists on a highway in Nevada. In the video, the truck driver tearfully told police he fell asleep at the wheel. ‚ÄúI guess I fell asleep. Because I don‚Äôt remember anything. I remember hitting those people,‚Äù Jordan Barson said tearfully in the video. Authorities now say a high level of methamphetamine was found in Barson‚Äôs system. Barson is facing multiple charges, including five counts of DUI resulting in death.

snippet.title: Sascha Huber X EHRENPFLAUME - Die nackte Wahrheit
snippet.description:
Am Ende hat es mich eiskalt erwischt. So sch√∂n der Tag mit @Sascha Huber und @Paulina Wallner auch angefangen hat, so anstrengend wurde er dann auch sp√§ter in Saschas "Folterkammer". Dieses Video ist aber in vielerlei Hinsicht speziell. Ich habe mit mit Justin und Julian, meinem Team, tats√§chlich 20 Stunden bei Paulina und Sascha Zuhause verbracht, da wir auch bei den beiden √ºbernachtet haben. Dadurch gibt mein Video wahrscheinlich einen Einblick in das Leben der beiden, den ihr so noch nirgendwo vorher gesehen habt. 2 Creator unter einem Dach, das ist auf jeden Fall spannend und ganz exklusiv erfahrt ihr auch noch, wie die beiden sich kennengelernt haben. Nur der Morgen des zweiten Tages fing f√ºr mich mit einer b√∂sen √úberraschung an. Wenn euch das Video gefallen hat, dann lasst einen Daumen nach oben da und schreibt flei√üig eure Meinung in die Kommentare. Ich w√ºnsche Euch allen frohe Weihnachten und bleibt gesund!

snippet.title: Frei.Wild - Schei√ü auf 2020 (Offizielles Video)
snippet.description:
Corona Tape II, Attacke ins Gl√ºck:
Ab 02.10.2020 beim Dealer deines Vertrauens!
ALLE Infos und Kauflinks unter: https://www.frei-wild.net/corona2
_______________

Erst sahen wir nur Wellen
Dann zogen Gewitterwolken auf
Es war wie im Alptraum
Wie im kalten Warteraum
Alles auf null, alles gecancelt
Wie ein Schock, wie ein Donnergrollen
Doch wir werden uns das alte Leben wieder holen

Die Fenster tief beschlagen und f√ºr keinen klare Sicht
Das Gl√ºck liegt auf der Strasse, nur diesmal lag es dort nicht
Nichts mehr planbar, das Vertraute au√üer Kraft
Nein dieses Jahr hat es uns allen schwer gemacht

Scheiss auf 2020
Jetzt beginnt die Weihnachtszeit
Das Fest der Familie
Niemals f√ºhlen wir es mehr als heute
Scheiss auf 2020
Z√ºndet eure Kerzen an
Denn diese Weihnachtszeit
Steht f√ºr einen Neuanfang
Scheiss auf 2020

So viel Unbekanntes
So viel Angst, war keinem vertraut
Die ganzen Blendgranaten
Haben uns so viel Schlaf geraubt
Jeder Kalender voller Fragezeichen
Und durchgestrichenen Tagen
Doch in der Hoffnung liegt die Kraft
Und ganz bestimmt nicht im Verzagen

Wann d√ºrfen wir wieder los?
Wieder zur√ºck in unsere Welt?
Die Welt vom L√§rm, des Lichts
Der Menschen in Freiheit die uns fehlt
Wollen wieder viele tausend H√§ndeIn den Himmel ragen sehen
Das hier war ein hartes Jahr
Doch wir werden bessere erleben

________________

snippet.title: "es ist genau das was du nicht tust" - JERY. | Offizielles Musikvideo
snippet.description:

https://open.spotify.com/track/0o28o24eKwD3a0WP1DiaYo?si=YqhU4BsgT4Sv_WIbh57Caw

Ich wollte mit diesem Song das Echte einer Verbindung zweier Menschen festhalten, keine "Fake-Love", alles ist so toll und didid... das ist f√ºr mich nicht das Gef√ºhl und die Realit√§t einer Beziehung. F√ºr mich sind es die Fehler, die Ecken und Kanten die den Menschen besonders machen und vor allem die Dinge, die der Partner "nicht macht". 
Deswegen der Titel "es ist genau das was du nicht tust". 
Ich habe das Gef√ºhl wir geben zu schnell auf, anstatt die schweren Zeiten zusammen durchzustehen, denn jedes mal wird gedacht, dass man im n√§chsten Partner noch jemanden findet der vielleicht 5 % besser zu einem passt, dem Partner einfach jede Freiheit zu schenken und dankbar zu sein, dass dieser Mensch immer wieder zur√ºck kommt, dass jeder seinen Weg geht, das Leben zu sp√ºren, sich wieder zu finden und zu sch√§tzen, dass man jemanden an seiner Seite hat, den man alles erz√§hlen kann und man sich die Erlebnisse teilt ist f√ºr mich
. . . . . 

Du bist nicht perfekt, sondern echt und GENAU darauf kommt es an!


Product: JERY. & MATTI die Traveler
Lyrics :  JERY.
Mix & Master : Stefan Heger
vocals Co. Product: Vase Simeon
Instrumentalist: Lennard Eggers 

Falls ihr lust habt, kommt gerne auf Instagram vorbei, dort findet ihr alles √ºber meine Zeit unterwegs im Van,  ich freue mich auf euch :) und schreibt mir gerne, wie euch der Song gef√§llt!  LIEBE.

Folgt mir auf:
‚ñ∫ Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/jeremygrube

Auf dem Weg mit dem Van durch die Welt, entsteht in meinem Van die Musik. 
das reisen zeigt mir das leben ohne Filter, und genau da finde ich meine Antworten.

snippet.localized.title: "es ist genau das was du nicht tust" - JERY. | Offizielles Musikvideo
snippet.localized.description:
Ihr k√∂nnt den Song Absofort auch √ºberall streamen: )

https://open.spotify.com/track/0o28o24eKwD3a0WP1DiaYo?si=YqhU4BsgT4Sv_WIbh57Caw

Ich wollte mit diesem Song das Echte einer Verbindung zweier Menschen festhalten, keine "Fake-Love", alles ist so toll und didid... das ist f√ºr mich nicht das Gef√ºhl und die Realit√§t einer Beziehung. F√ºr mich sind es die Fehler, die Ecken und Kanten die den Menschen besonders machen und vor allem die Dinge, die der Partner "nicht macht". 
Deswegen der Titel "es ist genau das was du nicht tust". 
Ich habe das Gef√ºhl wir geben zu schnell auf, anstatt die schweren Zeiten zusammen durchzustehen, denn jedes mal wird gedacht, dass man im n√§chsten Partner noch jemanden findet der vielleicht 5 % besser zu einem passt, dem Partner einfach jede Freiheit zu schenken und dankbar zu sein, dass dieser Mensch immer wieder zur√ºck kommt, dass jeder seinen Weg geht, das Leben zu sp√ºren, sich wieder zu finden und zu sch√§tzen, dass man jemanden an seiner Seite hat, den man alles erz√§hlen kann und man sich die Erlebnisse teilt ist f√ºr mich
. . . . . 

Du bist nicht perfekt, sondern echt und GENAU darauf kommt es an!


Product: JERY. & MATTI die Traveler
Lyrics :  JERY.
Mix & Master : Stefan Heger
vocals Co. Product: Vase Simeon
Instrumentalist: Lennard Eggers 

Falls ihr lust habt, kommt gerne auf Instagram vorbei, dort findet ihr alles √ºber meine Zeit unterwegs im Van,  ich freue mich auf euch :) und schreibt mir gerne, wie euch der Song gef√§llt!  LIEBE.

Folgt mir auf:
‚ñ∫ Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/jeremygrube

Auf dem Weg mit dem Van durch die Welt, entsteht in meinem Van die Musik. 
das reisen zeigt mir das leben ohne Filter, und genau da finde ich meine Antworten.
Ich m√∂chte mit euch in der Musik auf reisen gehen, alles erleben und alles teilen.

snippet.title: Witwe mit 36 - Marias erste Schritte in ein neues Leben | WDR Doku
snippet.description:
‚ÄûSein Tod ist gar nicht mehr das Schlimmste, obwohl ich meinen Mann unendlich vermisse‚Äú, sagt die 36j√§hrige Maria heute. ‚ÄúViel schlimmer sind die Wunden, die der Krebs in unserer Familie hinterlassen hat.‚Äú Die jahrelange Krankheit ihres Mannes Andrea Bizzotto hat sie und ihre beiden Kinder Fynn (14) und Giulia (3) ver√§ndert.

Im ersten halben Jahr nach seinem Tod am 1. M√§rz 2019 √ºberrollt Maria die B√ºrokratie: Beerdigung, Urkunden, Antr√§ge... dann st√ºrzt sie sich in Arbeit, um ein Buch, das ihr italienischer Mann noch kurz vor seinem Tod geschrieben hat, auf Deutsch herauszubringen und Lesungen damit zu machen. Und jetzt? Ihr wird klar, die kleine Wohnung steckt voller Erinnerungen an schmerzliche Situationen mit ihrem sterbenskranken Mann. Auch die alte Arbeitsstelle passt nicht mehr zu ihr. Sie braucht eine neue Umgebung ‚Äì und einen neuen Job. Maria muss den Schritt in ein neues Leben wagen und gleichzeitig ihren Kindern Giulia (3) und Fynn (14) genug Stabilit√§t geben, damit sie wieder Vertrauen ins Leben gewinnen. Wie geht das zusammen? 

Nach der Reportage ‚ÄûDas will ich Dir noch sagen‚Äú (WDR 2019) √ºber Maria und ihren Mann Andrea Bizzotto, der in seinen letzten Lebensmonaten noch einen italienischen Bestseller schrieb, haben wir Maria und ihre Kinder ein weiteres Jahr mit der Kamera begleitet. Die Alleinerziehende ist neue Wege gegangen ‚Äì ohne ihren Mann.

üíö Hier geht es zum ersten Film √ºber Maria und Andrea:  https://youtu.be/hRaNu4DdCco

snippet.description: On December 9, 2020, Starship serial number 8 (SN8) completed a high-altitude flight test as it successfully ascended, transitioned propellant, and demonstrated a first-of-its-kind controlled aerodynamic descent and landing flip maneuver ‚Äì which will enable landing where prepared surfaces or runways do not exist, including the Moon, Mars, and beyond.

snippet.title: Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE
snippet.description:
Did Dream Fake His Speedrun - RESPONSE , I'm sure a lot of you have been waiting for this...

This video I go over a recent video made by the Speedrun Mod team that claims that the odds that I got a series of drops over the span of a week is 1 in 7.5 trillion, and therefore came to the conclusion that I must have cheated. This video is meant to refute these claims. I encourage everyone to watch until the end, especially if they watched the original video.

In this video we hear from a statistical expert with a PhD that wrote a 19 page analysis on what the mods did wrong. I also disprove some of the claims made in the original video. All relevant information should be viewable below.

Although I would have loved to attempt to refute the math myself, I suck at math and would have looked like a complete idiot. So, that's where an expert comes in.

Expert's Report & Analysis - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yfLURFdDhMfrvI2cFMdYM8f_M_IRoAlM/view?usp=sharing

World File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pfA1HVWkROlFRG4egWh0GYV5SpbJGozR/view?usp=sharing

Tutorial for viewing level.dat, go to https://irath96.github.io/webNBT/ , and upload the "level.dat" file from the folder there. You can see the raw contents on the right, and an easy to use GUI on the left.

Jar File - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OEuu6PWAbhYo3BlUT2hL8mM_aiVPa9Yu/view?usp=sharing
This can be decompiled using a "Java Decompiler", but the modified dates can be verified on your computer.

Thank you to Willz for giving a statement in this video.

All revenue made from this video is being donated to the Minecraft Java Edition Speedrun Mod Team in order to fund development of an anti-cheater speedrun client.

Generally, speedrunning is a past time of mine and is a lot of fun. I mostly look forward to the funny moments with my friends, and the challenge that it presents for me.

Music From:
Audioblocks,
Lemmino - Cipher: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0q5PR1xpA0
Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio
